## Unique AMPEL360 Features

### BWB-Specific Operations
✅ Wide CG range management (15% vs 30% MAC)  
✅ Distributed passenger seating effects on balance  
✅ Non-linear pitching moment characteristics  
✅ Enhanced low-speed handling procedures  
✅ 30% fuel efficiency improvement documentation

### Hydrogen Fuel System Operations
✅ Cryogenic fuel handling procedures (-253°C)  
✅ 8,000 kg LH2 capacity data  
✅ 45-minute refueling procedures  
✅ Hydrogen leak detection and safety systems  
✅ Boil-off management and emergency procedures

### Fuel Cell Propulsion
✅ 10 MW total power output (4 × 2.5 MW stacks)  
✅ 55-60% efficiency characteristics  
✅ 3-second response time to full power  
✅ Zero direct emissions (H2O only)  
✅ Enhanced altitude performance

### CAOS Integration
✅ Real-time performance monitoring (1000+ parameters)  
✅ Neural network route optimization  
✅ Predictive operations analytics  
✅ Fleet learning and data sharing  
✅ AI-assisted flight planning  
✅ Automated compliance checking  
✅ Digital twin operations interface

