## Key Operational Benefits

### Efficiency
- **Fuel Efficiency**: 30% better than conventional (BWB) + 8-12% (CAOS)
- **Range**: 3,500 NM maximum with H2 fuel
- **Fuel Cell Efficiency**: 55-60% vs 40% for turbofans

### Environmental
- **Emissions**: Zero direct CO₂ (H2 combustion) + CO₂ capture capability
- **Noise**: 50% reduction vs conventional aircraft
- **Sustainability**: Green hydrogen compatible

### Operations
- **AI Optimization**: 8-12% fuel savings through CAOS
- **Predictive Maintenance**: 60% reduction in unscheduled events
- **Dispatch Reliability**: 99.7% vs 99.2% industry average
- **Crew Workload**: Reduced through AI assistance

